| comment "Dragnet [Ransomware]: dragnet-ransomware-2025-7364 — Recovery Inhibition (safepay)"
| comment "Status: experimental | Level: high | ID: 33072f88-f8bf-5d51-9a6c-f9b72bdd29d6"
